        <h2>Formula</h2>
        <p class="formula">
            $$ \text{Future Value} = P \cdot \left( \frac{(1 + r)^n - 1}{r}
            \cdot (1 + r) \right) + Q \cdot \left( \frac{(1 + r)^n - (1 +
            i)^n}{r - i} \cdot (1 + r) \right) $$
        </p>
        <table>
